<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Argentina Country Webpage</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/country.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/country-large.css">
    <script src="scripts/country.js" defer></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Ubuntu:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <meta name="author" content="Aaron Islas">
    <meta name="description" content="A Summary of Argentina with weather info, pictures, included with mobile and desktop views for practice.">
</head>
<header>
    <h1>Argentina</h1>
</header>
<body>
    <main>
        <section>
            <img src="images/buenos-aires-city.webp" alt="Buenos Aires City" class="hero-mobile-image">
        </section>
        <section class="data-section">
            <h2>Data</h2>
            <p>Area: 1.074 million km²</p>
            <p>Population: 45.8 million</p>
            <p>Capital: Buenos Aires</p>
            <p>Currency: Argentine peso (ARS)</p>
            <p>Language: Spanish</p>
            <p>Time Zone: Argentina Time (UTC-3)</p>
            <p>Calling Code: +54</p>
            <p>Internet TLD: .ar</p>
            <p>Weather: Average temperature ranges from 10°C to 30°C (50°F to 86°F)</p>
        </section>
        <section class="weather-section">
            <img src="images/sunny-day-svg-icon.svg" alt="Sunny Day Icon" class="weather-icon">
            <p>Temperature: 20 C</p>
            <p>Conditions: Clear Skies</p>
            <p>Wind: 10km/h</p>
            <p>Wind Chill: Placeholder For NOW<span id="calculateWindChill"></span></p>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
<footer>
    <p>&copy; Copyright: <span id="currentyear"></span></p>
    <p>Last Modification: <span id="lastModified"></span></p>
    <p>&#10070; Aaron Islas &#10070;</p>
</footer>
</html>